txt.en: 'We need to slap those living in the Delving into line. Now they are so bold as to come to the surface and stand at the outposts throughout the Ettenmoors.\n\n'Get out there and take those posts.'
'Bout time a [placeholder] like you pitched in around here.'
We need them outposts to get into the Delving of Frór. You look like the kind of maggot up to the task. Head into the Ettenmoors and capture one of those locations, maggot!
You have assisted in the capture of an outpost
Capture an outpost in the Ettenmoors

Make your way into the Ettenmoors and seek one of the outposts there. These can be found in the far south-west, overlooking the river near Hoarhallow, the near south north-west just beyond the river and north near the western entrance of the Isendeep Mine.\n\nYou have been tasked with capturing an outpost within the Ettenmoors. You should return to War-tyrant Akulhún when this is complete.
Return to War-tyrant Akulhún at Gramsfoot
The outpost is claimed for Angmar, return to War-tyrant Akulhún at Gramsfoot and tell him of your victory.
